Recommended license: MIT License.

Reason:

- Exile Creator Kit is intended to be an open-source creator utility.
- MIT is simple and permissive.
- MIT allows use, modification, redistribution, and commercial use with attribution.
- MIT is compatible with many Python desktop application workflows.

Important:

- This file is a placeholder until the project owner confirms the final license.
- Do not publish a public release until the final license text is selected.
- Bundled third-party components, including FFmpeg and FFprobe, keep their own licenses.
- The selected FFmpeg build may have LGPL or GPL obligations depending on how it was built.

